{"lemma":"حُزُمٌ","slug":"حُزُمٌ","root":"ح.ز.م","root_slug":"ح-ز-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ز-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7876","n7877"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D8%B2%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"belt, girth, waistband"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"girdle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cummerbund"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7876","headword_ar":"حَزْمٌ","root":"Hzm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prudence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discretion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precaution;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound management of one's affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking the sure course therein,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precaution, that it may not become beyond the power of management:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) said in a trad. to consist in evil opinion: and in another, in the asking counsel of people of judgment and obeying them: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good judgment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firmness of mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAzimN","text_ar":"حَازِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound management:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 33:) the first part thereof said by Aktham Ibn-Seyfee to be consultation: (Ham ibid:) from the same word as signifying the act of “ binding the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HizaAm","text_ar":"حِزَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", ” (Mgh,) or from this word as signifying the act of “ binding with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HzAm","text_ar":"حزام"},{"kind":"text","text":", ” and “ with the rope: ” (T, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazomapN","text_ar":"حَزْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a AlwaHaA='a mino TaEaAmi","text_ar":"اـِنَّ الوَحَا=ءَ مِنْ طَعَامِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHazomahi","text_ar":"الحَزْمَهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily quickness is of the food of prudence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], a prov., mentioned by Ibn-Kethweh, alluding to people's collecting themselves together and aiding one another, when they act with quickness, or sharpness, and vigour; and said in praise of him who thus acts. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a baAlHazomi","text_ar":"اَخَذَ بَالحَزْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and [sometimes]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlHazomi","text_ar":"فِى الحَزْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HwT","text_ar":"حوط"},{"kind":"text","text":") ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took the course prescribed by prudence, discretion, precaution,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good judgment; he used precaution:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a","text_ar":"اَخَذَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlv~iqapi","text_ar":"بِالثِّقَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took the sure course"},{"kind":"text","text":"in his affair].       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Elevated ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozamu","text_ar":"اَحْزَمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HayozuwmN","text_ar":"حَيْزُومٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged, ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yz, IB, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazomN","text_ar":"حَزْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more elevated than what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged, than what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HzonN","text_ar":"حزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 45:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and elevated ground, that is girt"},{"kind":"text","text":"(↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotazaAma","text_ar":"اِحْتَزَامَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by a torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged ground, having many stones, which are more rugged and rough and scabrous than those of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but the top of which is broad and long, extending to the length of two leagues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"less than that, which the camels do not ascend except by a road that it has:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Yaakoob, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzuwmN","text_ar":"حُزُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","T","TA","Mgh","Yz","IB"]},{"entry_id":"n7877","headword_ar":"حَزَمٌ","root":"Hzm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[in a horse (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozamu","text_ar":"اَحْزَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Largeness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fulness, of the sides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sides and belly and flank; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haDamN","text_ar":"هَضَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}